# 💠 KarMaTic Token Web dApp

This is the official decentralized web application for **KarMaTic (KMT)** on the **TON Blockchain**, designed to:

- Display token details and live price
- Allow wallet connection via **TON Connect**
- Facilitate token usage across Telegram Web Apps
- [In Progress] Swap KMT with TON through STON.fi integration

---

## 🔗 Live App

You can access the live dApp here:  
**[https://kmt-dev-panel.github.io/KMT-Token/kmt-wallet-connect.html](https://kmt-dev-panel.github.io/KMT-Token/kmt-wallet-connect.html)**

---

## ⚙️ Features

- 🔹 Real-time KMT token metadata and logo display  
- 🔹 Wallet connection via [Tonkeeper](https://tonkeeper.com/) and other TON-compatible wallets  
- 🔹 Jetton Master Address:  
  `EQBWSCOGJe17yWSh8zv7TiZiSf5lLY4ZI5FdmlvROcu4eDco`  
- 🔹 Rate from STON.fi pool: `1 TON ≈ 776 KMT`  
- 🔹 TVL: ~$11.26  
- 🔹 IPFS Logo:  
  `https://olive-cautious-gibbon-841.mypinata.cloud/ipfs/bafkreienac2lf6bnahv4vzvsmo53mbzzekbzdkygza5xuwubfivktsljo4`  
- 🔹 Manifest for TON Connect:  
  `https://kmt-dev-panel.github.io/KMT-Token/tonconnect-manifest.json`

---

## 📈 Usage Context

KMT token powers our internal ecosystem:

- 🔸 AI Personal Assistant Platform  
- 🔸 Minecraft SMP Server: `smp.kmt.icu`  
- 🔸 Telegram Web Apps with TON wallet integration  
- 🔸 In-app virtual store (coming soon)

KMT is **not intended for public trading or exchange listings**.

---

